        {
          "severity": "moderate",
          "criteria": "progressive weakness, some dependence, FVC 50-80%",
          "treatment": "NIPPV (bilevel) initiation. PEG tube insertion if dysphagia/weight loss. Symptom management: sialorrhea (glycopyrrolate, botox), spasticity (baclofen, tizanidine), cramps (quinine, magnesium)."
